ivardefs.name: matchType
ivardefs.desc: The operator to apply to the filter value when determining matches (Search modifiers).

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: The filter label (=key) as defined in the `Topic.canFilterBy.name`  element.

ivardefs.name: value
ivardefs.desc: The literal value or resource path as is legal in search - for example, "Patient/123" or "le1950".

properties.desc: The filter properties to be applied to narrow the topic stream.  When multiple filters are applied, evaluates to true if all the conditions are met; otherwise it returns false.   (i.e., logical AND).
